# Sen (@xensenx)

CS Engineering Student | Full-Stack Developer | Graphic Designer

I am a developer focused on building local-first AI applications, productivity ecosystems, and tools with minimalist, professional aesthetics. I specialize in bridging complex logic with clean, highly functional interfaces.

### What I am working on

* **Local-First Productivity:** Developing Proxen, an ecosystem designed for seamless, private task management.
* **Document Intelligence:** Building robust document vaults with local AI classification and custom OCR tools (Tesseract-OCRStudio).
* **Workflow Automation:** Creating automated system Git backup solutions and custom Obsidian plugins.
* **AI Integration:** Experimenting with comprehensive LLM interfaces and persona-based chat architectures (LLM_Chat, ProChats).

### Technical Arsenal

* **Core:** JavaScript, Python
* **Web & Design:** HTML/CSS, Minimalist UI/UX, Graphic Design
* **Domains:** Full-Stack Development, Local AI Implementation, System Automation
